# Paths Fern's Python generator must leave alone on every regen. Hand-written
# helpers and their tests live under stable paths so users can import them
# across releases without Fern overwriting the implementation. Keep this list
# narrow so Fern can keep regenerating sibling tests (conftest.py, utils/,
# test_aiohttp_autodetect.py, custom/, etc.) on each release.
src/truefoundry_gateway_sdk/helpers/
tests/test_merge_assistant_message.py
.github/workflows/ci.yml
